text: Lake San Marcos is a census-designated place (CDP) in the North County region of the San Diego metropolitan area. It is nominally independent of San Marcos proper. It is a resort-based community surrounding the Lake San Marcos reservoir. It is located at (33.122562, -117.209411). ==References== Category:Census-designated places in California Category:Settlements in San Diego County, California
title: Lake San Marcos, California
